
  ZORBA INSTALLATION OVERVIEW

  Required libraries
  ------------------
  
   LIBXML2 2.2.16 or higher (http://xmlsoft.org/ ) 
   ICU 3.2 (http://www.icu-project.org/
   BOOST 1.34 (http://www.boost.org/)
    -boost_program_options
    -boost_date_time
    -boost_filesystem
    -boost_program_options
   XERCES 2.8.0 (http://xerces.apache.org/xerces-c/)
   CURL 7.16 (http://curl.haxx.se/)
   ICONV 1.12 (http://www.gnu.org/software/libiconv/)
   MAPM ???
   Optional:
   FLEX 2.5.33 http://flex.sourceforge.net/
   
